<Paragraph>
When there is a need to summarize large reports, Excel allows you to summarize data through pivot table insertion. Excel 2007 supplies various built-in styles for pivot tables, allowing the creation of pivot tables with rich formats and more flexibility in summarizing reports. 
</Paragraph>

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">Features:</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>
<List> 
<ListItem><Paragraph>Create a pivot table from template data</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Customize the pivot table with various properties</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Format the pivot table with built-in styles</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph><Bold>Note:</Bold> This feature is currently not supported for the .xls format.</Paragraph>

